<p><a href="https://rubygems.org/gems/jekyll-theme-persephone"><img src="https://badge.fury.io/rb/jekyll-theme-persephone.svg" alt="Gem Version" /></a></p>

<p>Persephone is a minimal Jekyll theme designed for personal blog and your personal books/documents.</p>

